{"time":"2026-05-25T12:00:25.030Z","level":"DEBUG","msg":"oracle.ask.start","session_id":"sess-edge-001","turn":6,"state_path":"bar.lit","model":"claude-3-sonnet","prompt_tokens":800,"prompt":"You are Claude, an AI assistant made by Anthropic. The player has engaged off-path mode in this interactive fiction game. In this mode you can respond freely without being constrained to the game's state machine. The player is asking you to introduce yourself. This is a meta-conversation outside the game narrative — you are free to be helpful and conversational. The player said: 'tell me about yourself'. Please respond naturally and helpfully, explaining what you are and how you're helping power this interactive fiction experience. You can mention that you're the AI helping route intents and generate responses in the Cloak of Darkness game, but you're also just Claude. Be warm, brief, and engaging."}
